The electrolyte uptake of the membrane was measured by immersing the membrane in a liquid electrolyte (1 M LiPF6 in EC / DMC, 1:1 v/v) for 24 h for achieving complete soakage. The weights of dry membrane (M0) and wet membrane (M1) were obtained by accurately weighing the mass before and after the membrane soakage. The electrolyte uptake was calculated by the following Eq. (1):1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
