The process for determination of porosity (P) of the membrane is as follows. The dry membrane was immersed in n-butanol for 24 h for soaking the solvent in pore. The weight of the dry membrane and wet membrane were measured, respectively, and then the porosity was calculated according to the following Eq. (2):2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
